      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p>\n<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a large knob of<strong> butter</strong> over a medium-high heat</p>\n<p>Drain the<strong> sweetcorn</strong></p>\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>drained sweetcorn</strong> and cook for 7 min, stirring occasionally, until golden</p>",
